      • initialize

        public void initialize​(java.net.URL url,
                       java.util.ResourceBundle resourceBundle)
        Initializes the page. LAMBDA function here sets a variable with the selected date and it calls the radiobuttonChanged method to force that block of code to run. Otherwise I would need to write some callback method that would require a lot more work to get working. This LAMBDA lets me do it in about 5 lines of code.

        initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
